The code reads in the data file line by line. The measurement data for each line gets pushed onto a `measurement_pack_list`. The ground truth <span class="mathquill">[p_x, p_y, v_x, v_y]</span> for each line in the data file gets pushed onto`ground_truth`so RMSE can be calculated later from `tools.cpp`.

